Project Orion

Server management software

Descriptions of the software:

Version 1

1. Monitor the free HDD space and partitions
2. List all users, logged users
3. List installed packages

Verison 2

1. Send e-mails when user is logged in, HDD is full
2. running processes
3. Add remove packages

Version 3

1. Monitor network activity - upload and download speed, traffic per day
2. Panel for creating users, ftp accounts and etc.

Version 4

1. Send data to remote server
